"For a complete list of supported clients and features, see "
"xref:client-configuration:supported-features.adoc[]."
msgstr ""
"Per obtenir una llista completa de clients i característiques compatibles, "
"vegeu xref:client-configuration:supported-features.adoc[]."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-config-overview.adoc:6
