msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-pubcloud.adoc:18
msgid ""
"For instructions on registering {productname} to {scc}, see "
"xref:installation-and-upgrade:server-setup.adoc[]."
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-pubcloud.adoc:19
#, no-wrap
msgid "Register clients"
msgstr "Registra clients"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-pubcloud.adoc:20
msgid ""
"In the {productname} {webui}, navigate to menu:Systems[Bootstrapping], then "
"fill in the ``Host``, ``SSH Port``, ``User``, and ``Password`` fields.  Make "
"sure you use stable FQDNs for the ``Host`` field, or {productname} cannot "
"find your host when your Public Cloud gives you a different short-lived "
"FQDNS."
msgstr ""
"A {productname} {webui}, navegueu al menú:Systems[Bootstrapping] i ompliu "
"els camps .Host., .SSH Port., .User. i .Password..  Assegureu-vos que "
"utilitzeu FQDN estables per al camp .Host., o {productname} no pot trobar el "
"vostre amfitrió quan el vostre Núvol Públic us proporciona un FQDNS de vida "
"curta diferent."

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-pubcloud.adoc:21
msgid ""
"If you are attempting to bootstrap traditional clients, check that you can "
"resolve the host name of the server while you are logged in to the client.  "
"You might need to add the FQDN of the server to [path]``/etc/hosts`` local "
"resolution file on the client.  Check using the [command]``hostname -f`` "
"command with the local IP address of the server."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-pubcloud.adoc:22
msgid ""
"Public cloud images usually do not allow SSH login with username and "
"password, but only SSH with a certificate.  If you want to use bootstrap "
"from the {webui}, you need to enable SSH login with username and SSH key.  "
"You can do this by navigating to menu:Systems[Bootstrapping] and changing "
"the authentication method."
msgstr ""
"Les imatges públiques al núvol normalment no permeten l'inici de sessió amb "
"el nom d'usuari i la contrasenya, sinó només SSH amb un certificat.  Si "
"voleu utilitzar bootstrap des de {webui}, heu d'habilitar l'inici de sessió "
"SSH amb el nom d'usuari i la clau SSH.  Podeu fer-ho navegant al "
"menú:Sistemes[Bootstrapping] i canviant el mètode d'autenticació."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-pubcloud.adoc:23
msgid ""
"If your cloud provider is Microsoft Azure, you can log in with username and "
"password.  To do this, you need to allow the AzureUser to run commands as "
"root without a password.  To do this, open the "
"[path]``/etc/sudoers.d/waagent`` file, and add or edit this line:"
msgstr ""
"Si el vostre proveïdor al núvol és Microsoft Azure, podeu iniciar sessió amb "
"el nom d'usuari i la contrasenya.  Per fer-ho, heu de permetre que "
"l'AzureUser executi ordres com a root sense contrasenya.  Per a fer-ho, "
"obriu el fitxer [camí] the/etc/sudoers.d/waagent, i afegiu o editeu aquesta "
"línia:"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-pubcloud.adoc:24
#, no-wrap
msgid "AzureUser ALL=(ALL) NOPASSWD: ALL\n"
msgstr "AzureUser ALL ALL(ALL) NOPASSWD: ALL\n"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-pubcloud.adoc:25
msgid ""
"Allowing the AzureUser to run commands as root without a password carries a "
"security risk.  Use this method for testing only.  Do not do this for "
"production systems."
msgstr ""
"Permetre que l'AzureUser executi ordres com a root sense contrasenya "
"comporta un risc de seguretat.  Utilitzeu aquest mètode només per a provar-"
"lo.  No ho facis per als sistemes de producció."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-pubcloud.adoc:26
msgid ""
"When the bootstrap process has completed successfully, your client is listed "
"at menu:Systems[System List]."
msgstr ""
"Quan el procés d'arrencada s'ha completat correctament, el vostre client es "
"llista al menú:Systems[Llista de sistema]."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-pubcloud.adoc:27
msgid ""
"If you want more control over the process, have to register many clients, or "
"are registering traditional clients, create a bootstrap script.  For more "
"information, see xref:client-configuration:registration-bootstrap.adoc[]."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-pubcloud.adoc:28
msgid ""
"For Salt clients and even more control over the process, executing single "
"commands on the command line can be useful.  For more information, see "
"xref:client-configuration:registration-cli.adoc[]."
msgstr ""
"Per als clients de Salt i encara més control sobre el procés, l'execució "
"d'ordres individuals a la línia de comandes pot ser útil.  Per a més "
"informació, vegeu xref:client-configuration:registration-cli.adoc[]."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-pubcloud.adoc:29
msgid ""
"When registering clients launched from a public cloud image (for example, "
"AWS AMI), you need to do some additional configuration to prevent them from "
"over-writing each other.  For more information about registering clones, see "
"xref:administration:tshoot-registerclones.adoc[]."
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-pubcloud.adoc:30
#, no-wrap
msgid "Activation keys"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-pubcloud.adoc:32
msgid ""
"For more on activation keys, see "
"xref:client-configuration:activation-keys.adoc[]."
msgstr ""
"Per obtenir més informació sobre les claus d'activació, vegeu xref:client-"
"configuration:activation-keys.adoc[]."

#. type: Title =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-cdn.adoc:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Registering {rhel} Clients with CDN"
msgstr "S'estan registrant {rhel} clients amb CDN"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-cdn.adoc:2
msgid ""
"If you are running {rhel} clients directly, rather than using {sleses}, you "
"need to use Red Hat sources to retrieve and update packages.  This section "
"contains information about using the {redhat} content delivery network (CDN) "
"to register traditional and Salt clients running {rhel} operating systems."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-cdn.adoc:3
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-cdn.adoc:16
msgid ""
"For information about using {redhat} update infrastructure (RHUI) instead, "
"see xref:client-configuration:clients-rh-rhui.adoc[]."
msgstr ""
"Per obtenir informació sobre l'ús de la infraestructura d'actualització de "
"{redhat} (RHUI) vegeu xref:client-configuration:clients-rh-rhui.adoc[]."

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-cdn.adoc:4
msgid ""
"{rhel} clients are based on {redhat} and are unrelated to {sleses}, RES, or "
"{sles}.  You are responsible for arranging access to {redhat} base media "
"repositories and {rhela} installation media, as well as connecting "
"{productname} Server to the {redhat} content delivery network.  You must "
"obtain support from {redhat} for all your {rhela} systems.  If you do not do "
"this, you might be violating your terms with {redhat}."
msgstr ""

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-cdn.adoc:5
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-rhui.adoc:6
msgid ""
"Traditional clients are available on {rhel}{nbsp}6 and 7 only.  "
"{rhel}{nbsp}8 clients are supported as Salt clients."
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-cdn.adoc:6
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-rhui.adoc:7
#, no-wrap
msgid "Import Entitlements and Certificates"
msgstr "Importa drets i certificats"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-cdn.adoc:7
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-rhui.adoc:8
msgid ""
"{redhat} clients require a {redhat} certificate authority (CA) and "
"entitlement certificate, and an entitlement key."
msgstr ""
"{redhat} clients requereixen una autoritat de certificat {redhat} (CA) i un "
"certificat de dret, i una clau de dret."

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-cdn.adoc:8
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-cdn.adoc:18
msgid ""
"Entitlement certificates are embedded with expiration dates, which match the "
"length of the support subscription.  To avoid disruption, you need to repeat "
"this process at the end of every support subscription period."
msgstr ""
"Els certificats de drets estan incrustats amb dates de caducitat, que "
"coincideixen amb la durada de la subscripció de suport.  Per evitar "
"interrupcions, heu de repetir aquest procés al final de cada període de "
"subscripció d'assistència."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-cdn.adoc:9
msgid ""
"{redhat} supplies a subscription manager tool to manage subscription "
"assignments.  It runs locally to track installed products and "
"subscriptions.  Clients must be registered with the subscription manager to "
"obtain certificates."
msgstr ""
"{redhat} proporciona una eina de gestor de subscripcions per gestionar les "
"assignacions de subscripcions.  S'executa localment per fer un seguiment "
"dels productes i subscripcions instal·lades.  Els clients han d'estar "
"registrats al gestor de subscripcions per obtenir certificats."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-cdn.adoc:10
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-rhui.adoc:9
msgid ""
"{redhat} clients use a URL to replicate repositories.  The URL changes "
"depending on where the {redhat} client is registered."
msgstr ""
"{redhat} clients utilitzen un URL per replicar repositoris.  L'URL canvia "
"depenent d'on estigui registrat el client {redhat}."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-cdn.adoc:11
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-rhui.adoc:10
msgid "{redhat} clients can be registered in three different ways:"
msgstr "{redhat} clients es poden registrar de tres maneres diferents:"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-cdn.adoc:12
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-rhui.adoc:11
msgid "{redhat} content delivery network (CDN) at redhat.com"
msgstr "{redhat} xarxa de lliurament de continguts (CDN) a redhat.com"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-cdn.adoc:13
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-rhui.adoc:12
msgid "{redhat} Satellite Server"
msgstr "{redhat} Servidor de satèl·lit"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-cdn.adoc:14
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-rhui.adoc:13
msgid "{redhat} update infrastructure (RHUI) in the cloud"
msgstr "{redhat} actualització de la infraestructura (RHUI) al núvol"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-cdn.adoc:15
msgid ""
"This guide covers clients registered to {redhat} CDN.  You must have at "
"least one system registered to the CDN, with an authorized subscription for "
"repository content."
msgstr ""
"Aquesta guia cobreix els clients registrats a {redhat} CDN.  Heu de tenir "
"almenys un sistema registrat al CDN, amb una subscripció autoritzada per al "
"contingut del repositori."

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-cdn.adoc:17
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-rhui.adoc:16
msgid ""
"Satellite certificates for client systems require a Satellite server and "
"subscription.  Clients using Satellite certificates are not supported with "
"{productname} Server."
msgstr ""
"Els certificats de satèl·lit per als sistemes clients requereixen un "
"servidor de satèl·lit i subscripció.  Els clients que usen certificats de "
"satèl·lit no són compatibles amb el servidor {productname}."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-cdn.adoc:19
msgid ""
"{redhat} supplies the subscription-manager tool to manage subscription "
"assignments.  It runs locally on the client system to track installed "
"products and subscriptions.  Register to redhat.com with "
"subscription-manager, then follow this procedure to obtain certificates."
msgstr ""
"{redhat} subministra l'eina de gestió de subscripcions per gestionar les "
"assignacions de subscripcions.  S'executa localment al sistema client per "
"fer un seguiment dels productes i subscripcions instal·lades.  Registra't a "
"redhat.com amb subscription-manager i segueix aquest procediment per obtenir "
"certificats."

#. type: Block title
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-cdn.adoc:20
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Registering Clients to Subscription Manager"
msgstr "Procediment: Registre de Clients al Gestor de Subscripcions"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-cdn.adoc:21
msgid ""
"On the client system, at the command prompt, register with the subscription "
"manager tool:"
msgstr ""
"Al sistema client, a l'indicador de comandes, registra't amb l'eina gestor "
"de subscripcions:"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-cdn.adoc:22
#, no-wrap
msgid "subscription-manager register\n"
msgstr "registre de subscripcions\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-cdn.adoc:23
msgid "Enter your {redhat} Portal username and password when prompted."
msgstr ""
"Introduïu el nom d'usuari i la contrasenya del portal {redhat} quan se us "
"demani."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-cdn.adoc:24
msgid "Run command:"
msgstr "Executa l'ordre:"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-cdn.adoc:25
#, no-wrap
msgid "subscription-manager activate\n"
msgstr "activa el gestor de subscripcions\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-cdn.adoc:26
msgid ""
"Copy your entitlement certificate and key from the client system, to a "
"location that the {productname} Server can access:"
msgstr ""
"Copieu el vostre certificat de dret i la clau del sistema client, a una "
"ubicació a la qual el servidor {productname} pot accedir:"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-cdn.adoc:27
#, no-wrap
msgid "cp /etc/pki/entitlement/ /<example>/entitlement/\n"
msgstr "cp /etc/pki/entitlement/ /<example>/entitlement/\n"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-cdn.adoc:28
msgid ""
"Your entitlement certificate and key both have a file extension of "
"[path]``.pem``.  The key also has [path]``key`` in the filename."
msgstr ""
"El vostre certificat de títol i la clau tenen una extensió de fitxer de "
"[path]..pem..  La clau també té [camí].clau in al nom de fitxer."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-cdn.adoc:29
msgid ""
"Copy the {redhat} CA Certificate file from the client system, to the same "
"web location as the entitlement certificate and key:"
msgstr ""
"Copieu el fitxer de certificat CA {redhat} del sistema client, a la mateixa "
"ubicació web que el certificat i la clau de títol:"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-cdn.adoc:30
#, no-wrap
msgid "cp /etc/rhsm/ca/redhat-uep.pem /<example>/entitlement\n"
msgstr "cp /etc/rhsm/ca/redhat-uep.pem /<example>/entitlement\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-cdn.adoc:31
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-rhui.adoc:29
msgid ""
"To manage repositories on your {redhat} client, you need to import the CA "
"and entitlement certificates to the {productname} Server.  This requires "
"that you perform the import procedure three times, to create three entries: "
"one each for the entitlement certificate, the entitlement key, and the "
"{redhat} certificate."
msgstr ""
"Per gestionar repositoris al vostre client {redhat}, heu d'importar la CA i "
"els certificats de dret al servidor {productname}.  Això requereix que "
"realitzeu el procediment d'importació tres vegades, per crear tres entrades: "
"una per al certificat de dret, la clau de dret i el certificat {redhat}."

#. type: Block title
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-cdn.adoc:32
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-rhui.adoc:30
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Importing Certificates to the Server"
msgstr "Procediment: Importació de certificats al servidor"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-cdn.adoc:33
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-rhui.adoc:31
msgid ""
"On the {productname} Server {webui}, navigate to "
"menu:Systems[Autoinstallation > GPG and SSL Keys]."
msgstr ""
"Al servidor {productname} {webui}, navegueu al menú:Systems[Autoinstallation "
"]. GPG and SSL Keys]."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-cdn.adoc:34
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-rhui.adoc:32
msgid ""
"Click btn:[Create Stored Key/Cert] and set these parameters for the "
"entitlement certificate:"
msgstr ""
"Feu clic a btn:[Crea una clau emmagatzemada/Cert] i establiu aquests "
"paràmetres per al certificat de títol:"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-cdn.adoc:35
msgid ""
"In the [guimenu]``Description`` field, type "
"[systemitem]``Entitlement-Cert-date``."
msgstr "Al camp [guimenu].Descripció., escriviu [systemitem].títol-Cert-date.."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-cdn.adoc:36
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-cdn.adoc:41
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-cdn.adoc:46
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-rhui.adoc:34
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-rhui.adoc:39
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-rhui.adoc:44
msgid "In the [guimenu]``Type`` field, select [systemitem]``SSL``."
msgstr "Al camp [guimenu].Tipus., seleccioneu [systemitem].SSL.."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-cdn.adoc:37
msgid ""
"In the [guimenu]``Select file to upload`` field, browse to the location "
"where you saved the entitlement certificate, and select the [path]``.pem`` "
"certificate file."
msgstr ""
"Al camp [guimenu].Selecciona fitxer per pujar., navegueu fins a la ubicació "
"on heu desat el certificat de títol i seleccioneu el fitxer de certificat "
"[path]..pem.."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-cdn.adoc:38
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-cdn.adoc:43
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-cdn.adoc:48
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-rhui.adoc:36
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-rhui.adoc:41
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-rhui.adoc:46
msgid "Click btn:[Create Key]."
msgstr "Feu clic a btn:[Crea una clau]."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-cdn.adoc:39
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-rhui.adoc:37
msgid ""
"Click btn:[Create Stored Key/Cert] and set these parameters for the "
"entitlement key:"
