#: modules/client-configuration/pages/vhm-azure.adoc:15
msgid ""
"In the [guimenu]``Subscription ID`` field, type the subscription ID found in "
"[path]``Azure portal > Services > Subscriptions`` page."
msgstr ""
"Al camp [guimenu].ID de subscripció., escriviu l'ID de subscripció que es "
"troba a la pàgina [path].Portal segur . Serveis . Subscripcions.."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/vhm-azure.adoc:16
msgid ""
"In the [guimenu]``Application ID`` field, type the application ID that you "
"collected when you registered the application."
