#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/vhm-azure.adoc:18
msgid ""
"In the [guimenu]``Secret Key`` field, type the secret key associated with "
"the Azure instance."
msgstr ""
"Al camp [guimenu].Clau secreta., escriviu la clau secreta associada a la "
"instància d'Azure."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/vhm-azure.adoc:19
msgid ""
"In the [guimenu]``Zone`` field, type the zone your VM is located in. For "
"example, for West Europe, enter [path]``westeurope``."
