"Podeu utilitzar un gestor d'amfitrió virtual (VHM) per recollir instàncies "
"de Google Compute Engine (GCE)."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/vhm-gce.adoc:5
msgid ""
"The VHM you create needs to have the correct permissions assigned to access "
"the GCE VM."
